%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress%20-%20the%20two%20principal%20rival%20parties%20at%20the%20national%20level%20-%20asking%20them%20to%20explain%20the%20comments%20made%20by%20their%20star%20campaigners%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%20The%20comments%20allegedly%20violate%20the%20poll%20code.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJP%20Nadda%20and%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20have%20to%20submit%20their%20responses%20by%201%20am%20on%20Monday%2C%20two%20days%20before%20polls%20close%20for%20Maharashtra%20and%20Jharkhand%20(which%20will%20be%20conducting%20round%20two%20of%20polling).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20had%20filed%20a%20complaint%20on%20November%2011%20against%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20claiming%20that%20the%20Congress%20leader%20%26quot%3Bfalsely%20accused%20other%20states%20of%20stealing%20and%20snatching%20alleged%20opportunities%20from%20the%20State%20of%20Maharashtra%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20speech%20on%20November%206.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRahul%20Gandhi%20with%20his%20statements%20is%20inciting%20the%20youths%20of%20Maharashtra%20which%20is%20immensely%20dangerous%20for%20the%20unity%20and%20integrity%20of%20the%20nation.%20As%20only%20expected%20and%20in%20line%20with%20his%20typical%20pattern%20of%20campaigning%20and%20general%20conduct%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20speech%20was%20full%20of%20falsehood%20and%20lies%2C%20intending%20to%20create%20disaffection%2C%20enmity%20and%20ill-will%20between%20the%20states%20of%20Union%20of%20India.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20with%20his%20misleading%20statement%20has%20tried%20to%20create%20a%20divide%20between%20the%20people%20of%20Maharashtra%20and%20Gujarat%20%26amp%3B%20other%20states%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20BJP%20in%20its%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20in%20a%20counter-complaint%20on%20November%2013%20alleged%20that%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20delivered%20a%20%26quot%3Bslew%20of%20false%2C%20divisive%2C%20malicious%2C%20and%20slanderous%20statements%20about%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20(INC)%20and%20its%20allies%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20his%20speech%2C%20Amit%20Shah%20alleged%20that%20the%20INC%20and%20its%20allies%20were%3B%20(a)%20against%20Scheduled%20Caste%20(SC)%2C%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(ST)%2C%20and%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs)%3B%20(b)%20promoting%20terrorism%20in%20the%20country.%20In%20what%20has%20become%20a%20common%20narrative%20across%20the%20BJP's%20campaign%20in%20Jharkhand%2C%20Amit%20Shah%20has%20also%20accused%20the%20INC%20of%20planning%20to%20take%20away%20reservations%20from%20members%20of%20the%20ST%2C%20SC%20and%20OBC%20communities%20and%20granting%20them%20to%20members%20of%20a%20particular%20religious%20minority%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Congress%20in%20its%20complaint.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20statements%20made%20by%20Amit%20Shah%20have%20been%20made%20with%20the%20sole%20intent%20of%20inciting%20voters%20on%20the%20grounds%20of%20religion%20and%20caste%3B%20in%20order%20to%20consolidate%20votes%20and%20inducing%20them%20into%20voting%20for%20the%20BJP%20by%20stoking%20communal%20insecurity%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20model%20code%20of%20conduct%20mandates%20that%20no%20party%20or%20candidate%20shall%20include%20in%20any%20activity%20which%20may%20aggravate%20existing%20differences%20or%20create%20mutual%20hatred%20or%20cause%20tension%20between%20different%20castes%20and%20communities%2C%20religious%20or%20linguistic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20specifies%20that%20criticism%20of%20other%20political%20parties%20shall%20be%20confined%20to%20their%20policies%20and%20programme%2C%20past%20record%20and%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731757620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F1j87nid8_amit-shah-rahul-gandhi-split_625x300_19_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felection-commission-seeks-reply-from-mallikarjun-kharge-jp-nadda-on-rahul-gandhi-and-amit-shahs-speeches-7033749%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Election%20Commission%20on%20Saturday%20sought%20explanations%20from%20the%20party%20presidents%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress%20-%20the%20two%20principal%20rival%20parties%20at%20the%20national%20level%20-%20asking%20them%20to%20explain%20the%20comments%20made%20by%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felection-commission-seeks-reply-from-mallikarjun-kharge-jp-nadda-on-rahul-gandhi-and-amit-shahs-speeches-7033749%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Huge%20Blow%20For%20India%3A%20Star%20Fractures%20Thumb%2C%20Set%20To%20Miss%201st%20Aus%20Test%20-%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20were%20dealt%20a%20telling%20blow%20on%20Saturday%20after%20star%20top-order%20batter%20Shubman%20Gill%20sustained%20a%20left%20thumb%20fracture%20which%20is%20likely%20to%20rule%20him%20out%20of%20the%20opening%20Test%20of%20the%20Border-Gavaskar%20Trophy%20at%20the%20Optus%20Stadium%20in%20Perth%2C%20starting%20November%2022.%20Gill%2C%20one%20of%20the%20young%20heroes%20of%20India's%20last%20Border-Gavaskar%20Trophy%20triumph%2C%20is%20a%20batting%20mainstay%20and%20in%20case%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%20opts%20out%20of%20the%20first%20Test%2C%20India's%20top-order%20could%20look%20very%20thin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGill%20got%20hurt%20while%20fielding%20on%20the%20second%20day%20of%20the%20intra-squad%20match%20simulation.%20He%20was%20seen%20in%20considerable%20pain%20and%20immediately%20left%20the%20field%20for%20further%20scans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20BCCI%20source%20privy%20to%20the%20development%2C%20Gill%20has%20indeed%20fractured%20his%20left%20thumb%20and%20with%20less%20than%20a%20week%20left%20for%20the%20Test%20to%20start%2C%20it%20will%20be%20near%20impossible%20for%20the%20stylish%20right-hander%20to%20get%20fit%20in%20time%20for%20the%20opening%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20thumb%20fracture%20generally%20takes%20around%2014%20days%20to%20heal%20after%20which%20one%20is%20expected%20to%20start%20his%20regular%20net%20sessions.%20Since%20the%20second%20Test%20in%20Adelaide%20starts%20from%20December%206%2C%20there%20remains%20a%20possibility%20that%20he%20will%20get%20fit%20in%20time%20for%20that%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGill's%20absence%20could%20be%20massive%20for%20the%20national%20team%20as%20he%20is%20not%20only%20a%20stable%20number%20three%20batter%20but%20in%20case%20of%20Rohit's%20absence%2C%20he%20could%20be%20considered%20for%20opening%20the%20innings%20with%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20man%20in%20contention%2C%20Lokesh%20Rahul%2C%20has%20a%20bruised%20elbow%20after%20getting%20hit%20by%20a%20Prasidh%20Krishna%20short%20ball%20on%20the%20opening%20day%20of%20the%20intra-squad%20match%20and%20was%20forced%20to%20leave%20the%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul's%20bruised%20area%20needed%20icing%20and%20he%20didn't%20take%20the%20field%20on%20the%20second%20day%20of%20the%20match%20simulation%20on%20Saturday%20although%20it%20is%20being%20seen%20more%20as%20a%20precautionary%20measure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20case%20Gill%20is%20absent%2C%20Abhimanyu%20Easwaran%20could%20be%20in%20line%20for%20his%20Test%20debut%20as%20India%20do%20not%20have%20too%20many%20options%20left.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20if%20skipper%20Rohit%2C%20who%20was%20blessed%20with%20a%20baby%20boy%2C%20decides%20to%20join%20forces%20with%20three%20days%20of%20training%2C%20then%20it%20would%20be%20a%20different%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohammed%20Shami%2C%20who%20has%20bowled%20more%20than%2043.2%20overs%2C%20took%20seven%20wickets%20and%20scored%2037%20runs%20in%20Ranji%20Trophy%2C%20is%20certainly%20going%20to%20join%20the%20team%20before%20the%20second%20Test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20day%20of%20the%20match%20simulation%20will%20happen%20at%20the%20WACA%20on%20Sunday%20after%20which%20India%20A%20squad%2C%20barring%20reserve%20players%2C%20will%20be%20back%20to%20India%20and%20join%20their%20respective%20state%20teams%20for%20the%20Syed%20Mushtaq%20Ali%20Trophy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20squad%20will%20then%20move%20to%20Optus%20Stadium%20in%20Perth%20where%20they%20will%20have%20three%20net%20sessions%20from%20Tuesday%20to%20Thursday%20before%20going%20into%20the%20Test%20starting%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731757620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Flgsomctg_india-bcci_625x300_16_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Faustralia-vs-india-2024-25%2Fhuge-blow-for-india-shubman-gill-fractures-thumb-set-to-miss-1st-test-vs-australia-report-7033443%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20are%20set%20to%20take%20on%20Australia%20in%20a%20five-match%20Test%20series%2C%20starting%20November%2022%20in%20Perth.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Faustralia-vs-india-2024-25%2Fhuge-blow-for-india-shubman-gill-fractures-thumb-set-to-miss-1st-test-vs-australia-report-7033443%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explore%20Mike%20Tyson's%20cinematic%20journey%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731757410000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-115361348%2Cimgsize-31118.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fenglish%2Fexplore-mike-tysons-cinematic-journey-top-movies-and-documentaries-available-on-prime-video-and-netflix%2Farticleshow%2F115361194.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%