%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fpersonal-finance-editorial-standards%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20we%20rate%20products%20and%20services%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20help%20you%20make%20smart%20decisions%20with%20your%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jamie%20Valentino%20posing%20outside%20and%20smiling%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F673682d1fa0140cdd563a396%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJamie%20Valentino.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20Jamie%20Valentino%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThree%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20broke%20up%20with%20a%20wealthy%20ex%20and%20set%20out%20on%20my%20own%2C%20and%20it%20was%20a%20wake-up%20call.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EI%20realized%20I%20had%20tied%20up%20not%20knowing%20about%20money%20in%20my%20identity%2C%20and%20I%20had%20to%20stop%20relying%20on%20him.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EI%20may%20miss%20the%20glamour%20that%20my%20life%20with%20him%20afforded%20me%2C%20but%20I'm%20glad%20to%20be%20financially%20independent.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI%20recently%20marked%20three%20years%20since%20my%20official%20breakup%20with%20my%20ex%2C%20Brandon%2C%20and%20it%20took%20serious%20willpower%20not%20to%20wish%20him%20a%20happy%20anniversary.%20Our%20turbulent%2C%20on-and-off%20relationship%20was%20chaotic%20enough%20that%20I%20went%20celibate%20for%20a%20year%20afterward%2C%20but%20we've%20managed%20to%20look%20back%20on%20it%20with%20humor%20and%20a%20shared%20sense%20of%20accountability%20for%20our%20respective%20mistakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERegardless%2C%20I%20swore%20I'd%20never%20return%20to%20Brandon%2C%20and%20I%20kept%20my%20word.%20But%20I've%20been%20too%20afraid%20to%20cut%20him%20out%20of%20my%20life%20completely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it's%20not%20uncommon%20for%20exes%20to%20become%20friends%2C%20especially%20in%20LGBTQ%2B%20breakups%2C%20my%20ex%20got%20upset%20when%20I%20described%20our%20relationship%20as%20platonic.%20I%20felt%20obligated%20to%20remove%20myself%20from%20his%20life%20to%20help%20him%20make%20space%20in%20his%20heart%20for%20someone%20else%2C%20but%20I%20selfishly%20struggled%20with%20the%20reality%20of%20not%20having%20anyone%20to%20fall%20back%20on%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20financially.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMoving%20in%20with%20a%20wealthier%20partner%20made%20it%20easy%20to%20lose%20sense%20of%20the%20lifestyle%20I%20could%20afford%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20should've%20predicted%20it%20would%20be%20challenging%20to%20end%20communication%20with%20someone%20I've%20depended%20on%20so%20heavily%20%E2%80%94%20emotionally%2C%20financially%2C%20and%20for%20all%20the%20little%20joys%20that%20come%20with%20being%20with%20someone%20who%20treated%20my%20happiness%20like%20their%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20was%20that%20Brandon's%20controlling%20nature%20and%20short%20temper%20simultaneously%20became%20the%20source%20of%20my%20misery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20on%20that%20note%2C%20I%20landed%20in%20Tulum%20Pueblo%20in%20June%202021%2C%20seeking%20an%20escape%20from%20a%20household%20fueled%20by%20fights.%20Switching%20my%20expenses%20from%20dollars%20to%20pesos%20allowed%20me%20time%20to%20recalibrate%20my%20future%20without%20him.%20I%20didn't%20know%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Fbest-budgeting-apps%5C%22%3Ebudget%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20what%20I%20could%20afford%20because%20Brandon%20covered%20all%20our%20bills%20and%20then%20some.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20proud%20of%20myself%20for%20not%20letting%20financial%20comfort%20keep%20me%20in%20an%20unhappy%20relationship%20any%20longer.%20Yet%2C%20there%20I%20was%2C%20dragging%20my%20overpacked%20luggage%20aimlessly%20up%20the%20scorching%20streets%20%E2%80%94%20sweating%20from%20nerves%20and%20heat%20%E2%80%94%20wondering%20what%20the%20hell%20I%20was%20going%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20arrived%20at%20my%20monthly%20sublet%20ready%20to%20pave%20a%20new%20beginning%2C%20only%20to%20be%20met%20with%20a%20glare%20from%20my%20landlord.%20She%20had%20forgotten%20to%20mention%20that%20payment%20was%20cash%20only%20and%20still%20blamed%20me%20for%20not%20having%20it.%20I%20couldn't%20move%20in%20until%20I%20procured%20the%20money%2C%20which%20would%20take%20a%20few%20days%20due%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Fatm-withdrawal-limits%5C%22%3EATM%20withdrawal%20limits%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EEven%20after%20I%20left%20Brandon%2C%20he%20was%20the%20only%20person%20I%20felt%20comfortable%20asking%20for%20help%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20going%20to%20be%20homeless!%26quot%3B%20I%20panicked%20to%20Brandon%20on%20the%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20asking%20me%20to%20help%20you%20leave%20me%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20halfheartedly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20actually%20ask%20Brandon%20for%20help%2C%20but%20he%20wasn't%20wrong.%20I%20called%20him%20subconsciously%20(or%20maybe%20consciously)%20in%20times%20of%20trouble%2C%20knowing%20he'd%20try%20to%20find%20a%20solution.%20He%20suggested%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Fhow-to-send-money-to-someone-without-a-bank-account%5C%22%3Esending%20me%20money%20via%20Western%20Union%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20I%20could%20access%20immediately.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnexpectedly%2C%20he%20instructed%20me%20not%20to%20pay%20him%20back%2C%20advising%20me%20to%20save%20my%20funds%20for%20%3Cem%3Eanother%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Fwhat-is-an-emergency-fund%5C%22%3Eemergency%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20appeared%20he%20understood%20my%20situation%20better%20than%20I%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20I%20relied%20on%20Brandon's%20help%20to%20secure%20a%20roof%20over%20my%20head%20that%20night%2C%20I%20laid%20down%20and%20closed%20my%20eyes%2C%20convinced%20I%20didn't%20need%20him.%20Unfortunately%2C%20as%20I%20kept%20learning%2C%20life%20was%20more%20nuanced%20than%20my%20best%20intentions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20called%20Brandon%20when%20my%20phone%20was%20stolen%20while%20I%20was%20living%20in%20Colombia%20the%20following%20year%2C%20when%20my%20LASIK%20payment%20plan%20reached%20its%20grace%20period%20with%20interest%20piling%20up%20like%20an%20avalanche%2C%20and%20most%20pathetically%2C%20when%20I%20simply%20overspent%2C%20clinging%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Flifestyle-creep%5C%22%3Elifestyle%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20was%20no%20longer%20mine%2C%20even%20in%20pesos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMy%20problem%20was%20rooted%20in%20the%20fact%20I%20had%20never%20cared%20or%20learned%20about%20money%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20never%20learned%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Fhow-to-save-money%5C%22%3Ehow%20to%20save%20money%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20used%20to%20believe%20my%20aloof%20relationship%20with%20money%20was%20admirable.%20I%20didn't%20date%20Brandon%20because%20he%20was%20well-off%2C%20but%20it%20facilitated%20existing%20in%20the%20contradiction%20of%20not%20prioritizing%20money%20while%20treating%20it%20like%20no%20object.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20my%20millennial%20generation%20and%20Latin%20culture%20raised%20me%20on%20the%20values%20of%20hustling%20and%20earning%20my%20way.%20I'd%20never%20feel%20comfortable%20asking%20a%20family%20member%20or%20close%20friend%20for%20even%20a%20small%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Floans%5C%22%3Eloan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20Brandon%20was%20right%3A%20We%20were%20not%20platonic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20faced%20the%20reality%20that%20I%20was%20one%20of%20millions%20of%20Americans%20whose%20lives%20could%20be%20upended%20by%20suddenly%20needing%20to%20cough%20up%20a%20few%20thousand%20dollars.%20Letting%20go%20of%20Brandon%20would've%20replaced%20my%20safety%20net%20with%20concrete.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELet's%20be%20honest%3A%20Emotional%20support%20is%20abundant%20when%20you%20have%20people%20who%20care%20about%20you.%20However%2C%20when%20the%20problem%20is%20financial%2C%20even%20loved%20ones%20become%20like%20ostriches%2C%20burying%20their%20heads%20in%20the%20sand%20until%20the%20crisis%20ends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20way%20to%20avoid%20falling%20is%20knowing%20no%20one%20is%20there%20to%20catch%20you.%20Knowing%20that%20was%20how%20I%20made%20it%20on%20my%20own%20before%20I%20met%20Brandon.%20Whether%20I%20meant%20to%20or%20not%2C%20I%20needed%20to%20stop%20taking%20advantage%20of%20his%20unconditional%20love%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20returned%20permanently%20to%20U.S.%20soil%20this%20year%2C%20I%20began%20looking%20for%20an%20apartment.%20Once%20again%2C%20habit%20tempted%20me%20to%20call%20him%20since%20I%20needed%20a%20guarantor%20for%20the%20place%20I%20had%20my%20eye%20on.%20But%20I%20kept%20looking%2C%20determined%20to%20find%20the%20life%20that%20belonged%20to%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20less%20glamorous%20than%20I%20expected%2C%20but%20it%20was%20a%20more%20affordable%20price%20than%20my%20integrity%20or%20happiness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDon't%20know%20where%20to%20start%3F%20Consider%20a%20financial%20advisor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsmartasset.com%2Fretirement%2Ffind-a-financial-planner%3Futm_source%3Dbusinessinsider%26utm_medium%3Dcpc%26utm_campaign%3Dbus__falc_bicontent%26utm_content%3DBI%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFinding%20a%20financial%20advisor%3C%2Fa%3E%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20hard.%20SmartAsset's%20free%20tool%20matches%20you%20with%20up%20to%20three%20fiduciary%20financial%20advisors%20who%20serve%20your%20area%20in%20minutes.%20Each%20advisor%20has%20been%20vetted%20by%20SmartAsset%20and%20is%20held%20to%20a%20fiduciary%20standard%20to%20act%