%20parameter%20and%20say%20Maharashtra%20is%20doing%20well.%20It%20is%20a%20number%20of%20parameters%20over%20a%20period%20of%20time%20to%20decide%20whether%20the%20state%20is%20growing%20or%20sliding.%20I%20have%20with%20me%20data%20which%20shows%20that%20the%20growth%20of%20the%20state%20GDP%20has%20declined%20from%202022-2023%20to%202023-2024.%20Similarly%2C%20revenue%20deficit%20has%20ballooned%2C%20fiscal%20deficit%20has%20ballooned%2C%20agricultural%20growth%2C%20services%20sector%20growth%2C%20transport%2C%20trade%2C%20communications%20growth%20and%20construction%20growth%20have%20all%20fallen%20sharply%20as%20much%20as%203%25%20to%207-8%25%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20Union%20Finance%20Minister%2C%20in%20Mumbai%20ahead%20of%20the%20state%20polls%2C%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20goes%20to%20polls%20on%20November%2020.%20The%20votes%20will%20be%20counted%20on%20November%2023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20GEP%20(Gross%20Ecosystem%20Product)%20itself%20has%20declined%20from%209.4%25%20to%207.6%25.%20If%20this%20is%20the%20path%20Maharashtra%20is%20economy%20is%20going%20in%2C%20how%20can%20you%20say%20that%20Maharashtra%20is%20growing%20economically%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chidambaram%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGross%20Ecosystem%20Product%20(GEP)%20is%20an%20index%20that%20measures%20the%20economic%20value%20of%20nature's%20contributions%20to%20human%20well-being.%20It%20is%20modeled%20after%20the%20Gross%20Domestic%20Product%20(GDP)%20and%20is%20used%20to%20help%20achieve%20sustainable%20development%20by%20moving%20beyond%20conventional%20economic%20measures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20only%20talking%20about%20economically.%20It%20is%20not%20growing.%20It%20is%20slipping%20and%20as%20a%20result%20of%20that%20there's%20massive%20unemployment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsserting%20that%20talk%20of%20the%20state%20facing%20a%20%26quot%3Bmountain%20of%20debt%26quot%3B%20was%20a%20myth%2C%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20said%20Maharashtra's%20economy%20is%20worth%20Rs%2040%20lakh%20crore%2C%20of%20which%20just%20Rs%206-6.5%20lakh%20crore%20constitutes%20debt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20ruling%20coalition%20and%20its%20%241%20trillion%20economy%20promise%20for%20Maharashtra%2C%20Mr%20Chidambaram%20underlined%20that%20the%20important%20question%20to%20ask%20is%20%26quot%3Bwhen%26quot%3B%2C%20adding%20that%20without%20a%20set%20timeframe%20it%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bmeaningless%20statement%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%241%20trillion%20is%20a%20goalpost.%20As%20meaningless%20as%20the%20Union%20of%20India's%20goalpost%20of%20%245trillion.%20You%20will%20reach%20the%20goalpost%20whether%20there's%20a%20government%20or%20not.%20Whether%20you%20grow%20at%203%25%20or%205%25%20or%208%25%20or%2010%25.%20If%20you%20grow%2C%20you%20will%20reach%20the%20goalpost%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%2079-year-old%20Congress%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20it%2C%20the%20Congress%20leader%20said%20if%20you%20go%20from%20Mumbai%20to%20Pune%2C%20you%20will%20reach%20Pune%20whether%20you%20fly%20or%20drive%20or%20go%20in%20a%20bullock%20cart%20or%20go%20on%20a%20cycle%20or%20go%20walking.%20The%20point%2C%20said%20the%20Congress%20leader%2C%20is%20when.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20central%20government%20has%20shifted%20the%20%245trillion%20goalpost%203-4%20times.%20Now%20it%20is%20somewhere%20in%202026-2027%20or%202027-2028.%20If%20anybody%20claims%20I%20will%20reach%20%241trllion%2C%20you%20must%20say%20when.%20They%20don't%20say%20when.%20It's%20like%20saying%20my%20child%20will%20grow%20to%203%20feet.%20Every%20child%20will%20grow%20to%203%20feet.%20My%20child%20will%20grow%20to%204%20feet%2C%20of%20course%20a%203-foot%20high%20child%20will%20grow%20to%204%20feet%20.%20It's%20a%20meaningless%20statement%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Chidambaram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20Union%20Minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20slammed%20