orks%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EEli%20Lilly's%20retatrutide%20drug%20is%20administered%20the%20same%20way%20as%20the%20market%20leaders%20Ozempic%2C%20Wegovy%2C%20Mounjaro%2C%20and%20Zepbound%3A%20it's%20a%20once-weekly%20injection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat's%20unique%20is%20the%20substance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20semaglutide%20(the%20active%20ingredient%20in%20Ozempic%20and%20Wegovy)%2C%20it%20works%20on%20GLP-1%2C%20a%20hormone%20that%20regulates%20blood%20sugar%20and%20appetite.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20tirzepatide%20(the%20drug%20in%20Mounjaro%20and%20Zepbound)%2C%20it%20also%20works%20on%20GIP%2C%20a%20hormone%20that%20manages%20blood%20sugar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUniquely%2C%20retatrutide%20has%20an%20additional%20effect%2C%20mimicking%20another%20hormone%20called%20glucagon%2C%20which%20may%20help%20increase%20the%20body's%20energy%20use.%20The%20idea%20is%20that%20it%20promotes%20weight%20loss%20by%20not%20only%20curbing%20appetite%2C%20but%20also%20burning%20more%20calories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECurrent%20research%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nejm.org%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1056%2FNEJMoa2301972%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresults%20of%20mid-stage%20trials%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20patients%20taking%20retatrutide%20lost%20an%20average%20of%2058%20pounds%20in%2011%20months%2C%20more%20and%20faster%20weight%20loss%20than%20has%20been%20seen%20with%20drugs%20currently%20on%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETimeline%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ERetatrutide%20is%20currently%20being%20studied%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftrials.lilly.com%2Fen-US%2Ftrial%2F405675%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPhase%20III%20trials%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20are%20scheduled%20to%20be%20completed%20in%20early%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e636601d-d064-4676-851b-b8a28f3debbe%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20faster-acting%20weight-loss%20drug%20that%20could%20be%20a%20pill%20or%20injection%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy