0VK2735%20is%20expected%20to%20enter%20Phase%20II%20trials%20by%20the%20end%20of%20this%20year%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2277bb7c6c-1d1d-424d-aa59-728b114c2d15%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EEli%20Lilly%20is%20racing%20to%20get%20the%20first%20weight-loss%20pill%20on%20the%20market%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20it's%20interesting%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EEli%20Lilly%20may%20beat%20Viking%20Therapeutics%20to%20get%20the%20first%20oral%20GLP-1%20to%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20drug%20orforglipron%20appeals%20to%20patients%20who%20can't%20or%20don't%20want%20to%20use%20injected%20medications.%20It%20is%20also%20expected%20to%20be%20cheaper%2C%20since%20it's%20easier%20to%20produce%20(orforglipron%20isn't%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpeptides-growth-hormone-hgh-new-health-fad-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epeptide%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20other%20GLP-1%20drugs).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20clock%20is%20ticking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENovo%20Nordisk%20already%20has%20an%20oral%20semaglutide%20to%20treat%20type%202%20diabetes%2C%20sold%20under%20the%20brand%20name%20Rybelsus%2C%20and%20they're%20trialing%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fozempic-pill-semaglutide-helped-overweight-people-lose-weight-in-trial-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh-dose%20version%20of%20that%20pill%20that%20could%20be%20approved%20for%20weight%20loss%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20it%20works%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20active%20ingredient%20in%20the%20daily%20pill%20is%20a%20small%20molecule%20which%20slow%20digestions%20and%20manages%20blood%20sugar%20and%20insulin%2C%20similar%20to%20semaglutide%20(Ozempic%2C%20Wegovy).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECurrent%20research%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nejm.org%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1056%2FNEJMoa2302392%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EResults%20from%20Phase%20II%20trials%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20people%20taking%20orforglipron%20lost%20between%209.4%25%20and%2014.7%25%20of%20their%20body%20weight%2C%20on%20average%2C%20in%2036%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETimeline%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Current%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fclinicaltrials.gov%2Fstudy%2FNCT05869903%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elate-stage%20trials%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20expected%20to%20last%20into%202027.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221e386d6d-423a-4b83-b3c7-70231a9cd219%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENovo%20Nordisk%20is%20touting%20a%20stronger%20alternative%20to%20Ozempic%20that%20may%20be%20easier%20to%20produce%20at%20scale%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20it's%20interesting%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ECagriSema%20is%20a%20once-weekly%20injection%20that%20combines%20semaglutide%20(active%20ingredient%20in%20Ozempic%20and%20Wegovy)%20with%20a%20compound%20targeting%20another%20hormone%2C%20cagrilintide.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20combination%20is%20expected%20to%20help%20people%20lose%20significantly%20more%20weight%20than%20semaglutide%20alone%2C%20Novo%20Nordisk%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20it%20works%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ECagrilintide%20mimics%20the%20effects%20of%20a%20naturally-occurring%20hormone%20to%20regulate%20appetite%20and%20digestion%20and%20lower%20blood%20sugar.%20CagriSema%20adds%20it%20to%20the%20already-popular%20drug%20semaglutide%2C%20which%20itself%20helps%20manage%20hunger%20and%20blood%20sugar%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENovo's%20chief%20financial%20officer%20said%20in%20an%20earnings%20call%20that%20it%20would%20source%20cagrilintide%20from%20a%20third-party%20company%2C%20which%20could%20help%20with%20manufacturing.%20Supply%20issues%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuy-compounded-semaglutide-online-risks-wegovy-ozempic-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshortages%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20previously%20hampered%20its%20semaglutide%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECurrent%20research%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOne%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thelancet.com%2Fjournals%2Flancet%2Farticle%2FPIIS0140-6736(23)01163-7%2Fabstract%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eearly%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20patients%20lost%20more%20weight%20on%20CagriSema%20(about%2015%25%20weight%20loss%20over%2032%20weeks)%20than%20either%20semaglutide%20or%20cagrilintide%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Novo%20Nordisk%20executive%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fbusiness%2Fhealthcare-pharmaceuticals%2Fnovo-nordisk-says-its-experimental-drug-cagrisema-has-similar-side-effects-2024-11-06%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReuters%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20projections%20from%20the%20data%20suggest%20it%20could%20help%20people%20lose%20even%20more%2C%20up%20to%2025%25%20of%20their%20weight%2C%20over%20a%20longer%20timeline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETimeline%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EPhase%20III%20clinical%20trials%20for%20Cagrisema%20are%20ongoing%20and%20slated%20to%20last%20until%20late%202025.%20The%20drug%20could%20be%20available%20in%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f9e2452f-a8fe-47e5-a61d-209a3b2b28b3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20longer-lasting%20monthly%20shot%20from%20Amgen%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20it's%20interesting%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EMariTide%2C%20from%20biotech%20company%20Amgen%2C%20could%20be%20a%20much%20longer-lasting%20treatment%20than%20current%20drugs.%20It%20only%20needs%20to%20be%20injected%20once%20a%20month%20%E2%80%94%20or%20even%20less%20frequently%20%E2%80%94%20compared%20to%20the%20once-weekly%20requirement%20for%20semaglutide%20and%20tirzepatide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLonger-acting%20versions%20of%20GLP-1%20medications%20offer%20the%20potential%20for%20greater%20convenience%20and%20potentially%20improved%20adherence%20and%20sustained%20use%20over%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20McGowan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20catch%20is%20whether%20side%20effects%20might%20last%20longer%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20it%20works%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EMariTide%20is%20similar%20to%20Mounjaro%20and%20Zepbound%20because%20it%20mimics%20GLP-1%20and%20GIP%20hormones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20difference%20is%20that%20MariTide%20dials%20down%20GIP%20receptor%20activity.%20Amgen%20says%20this%20makes%20it%20easier%20for%20the%20body%20to%20burn%20fat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20fascinating%20because%20it%20appears%20that%20both%20enhancing%20and%20opposing%20the%20GIP%20receptor%20influence%20weight%20regulation%2C%20which%20speaks%20to%20how%20little%20is%20still%20known%20about%20the%20actual%20weight-regulating%20mechanism%20of%20certain%20gut%20hormones%2C%26quot%3B%20McGowan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECurrent%20research%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EPatients%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3De053792e27a615fb7dda56aa0745b0c87c4f95e380ec169abcf45f1d1b11336c%26postID%3D673380d5d057d3e5c5d03443%26postSlug%3Dupcoming-glp1-weight-loss-drugs-to-watch-2024-11%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.nature.com%252Farticles%252Fs42255-023-00966-w%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esmall%20early-stage%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20lost%2014.5%25%20of%20body%20weight%20on%20average%20in%2012%20weeks.%20Those%20who%20got%20just%20a%20single%20dose%20lost%20an%20average%208.2%25%20of%20their%20body%20weight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETimeline%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EData%20from%20Phase%20II%20trials%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amgen.com%2Fnewsroom%2Fpress-releases%2F2024%2F10%2Famgen-reports-third-quarter-2024-financial-results%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexpected%20later%20this%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20planning%20is%20underway%20for%20Phase%20III%20trials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fupcoming-glp1-weight-loss-drugs-to-watch-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22