%2C%20that%20appears%20in%20the%20docuseries%20trailer.%20Seemingly%20upset%20by%20the%20legal%20action%2C%20Nayanthara%20responded%20by%20sharing%20an%20open%20letter%20addressed%20to%20Dhanush%20on%20her%20Instagram%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20excerpt%20from%20Nayanthara's%20letter%20read%2C%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20two%20long%20years%20of%20battling%20it%20out%20with%20you%20for%20an%20NOC%20(No%20Objection%20Certificate)%20and%20waiting%20for%20your%20approval%20for%20our%20Netflix%20documentary%20release%2C%20we%20finally%20decided%20to%20give%20up%2C%20re-edit%20and%20settle%20for%20the%20current%20version%20since%20you%20declined%20to%20permit%20the%20usage%20of%20Naanum%20Rowdy%20Dhaan%20songs%20or%20visual%20cuts%2C%20even%20the%20photographs%20to%20say%20the%20least%20despite%20multiple%20requests.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENayanthara%20also%20highlighted%20how%20this%20was%20%E2%80%9Can%20all-time%20low%E2%80%9D%20for%20Dhanush.%20The%20actress%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat's%20even%20more%20shocking%20is%20your%20legal%20notice%20after%20the%20release%20of%20the%20trailer%20of%20the%20Netflix%20Documentary.%20We%20were%20startled%20to%20read%20those%20lines%20wherein%20you%20questioned%20the%20usage%20of%20some%20videos%20(just%203%20seconds)%20which%20were%20shot%20in%20our%20personal%20devices%20and%20that%20too%20BTS%20visuals%20that%20are%20already%20very%20much%20publicly%20present%20on%20social%20media%20and%20claimed%20a%20sum%20of%20Rs.10%20crores%20as%20damages%20for%20the%20mere%203%20seconds.%20This%20is%20an%20all%20time%20low%20from%20you%20and%20speaks%20so%20much%20about%20your%20character.%20I%20wish%20you%20were%20half%20the%20person%20you%20portray%20to%20be%20on%20stage%20in%20audio%20launches%20in%20front%20of%20your%20innocent%20fans%20but%20clearly%20you%20do%20not%20practice%20what%20you%20preach%2C%20at%20least%20not%20for%20me%20and%20my%20partner.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDoes%20a%20Producer%20become%20an%20Emperor%20controlling%20the%20lives%2C%20freedom%20and%20liberty%20of%20all%20the%20persons%20in%20the%20set%3F%20Any%20deviation%20from%20the%20Emperor's%20dictum%20attracts%20legal%20ramifications%3F%E2%80%9D%20Nayanthara%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20a%20jibe%20at%20Dhanush%2C%20Nayanthara%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt's%20almost%20been%2010%20years%20since%20the%20release%20of%20the%20film%20and%20it%20is%20a%20long%20time%20for%20someone%20to%20continue%20to%20be%20this%20vile%20while%20wearing%20a%20mask%20in%20front%20of%20the%20world.%20I%20have%20not%20forgotten%20all%20the%20horrible%20things%20that%20you%20said%20about%20the%20film%20that%20was%20one%20of%20your%20biggest%20hits%20as%20a%20producer%20and%20a%20film%20that%20is%20loved%20by%20all%20even%20today.%20The%20words%20you%20said%20pre-release%20have%20left%20some%20unhealable%20scars%20to%20us%20already.%20I%20learnt%20through%20film%20circles%20that%20your%20ego%20was%20supremely%20hurt%20after%20the%20film%20became%20a%20blockbuster.%20Your%20displeasure%20over%20its%20success%20was%20perceptible%20even%20to%20common%20man%20through%20award%20functions%20connected%20with%20this%20film%20(Filmfare%202016).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENayanthara%20signed%20off%20by%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9COm%20Namah%20Shivaya.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERead%20her%20full%20letter%20below%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FDCbCgAgPIxW%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FDCbCgAgPIxW%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E