p%3EThe%2081-year-old%20iconic%20Howrah%20Bridge%20(Rabindra%20Setu)%20--%20that%20connects%20the%20cities%20of%20Kolkata%20and%20Howrah%20--%20will%20remain%20closed%20to%20traffic%20for%20five%20hours%20on%20the%20intervening%20night%20of%20Saturday%20and%20Sunday%20for%20a%20comprehensive%20health%20check-up%2C%20the%20Syama%20Prasad%20Mookerjee%20Port%20(SMP)%2C%20Kolkata%2C%20has%20notified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESMP%2C%20Kolkata%20is%20the%20custodian%20of%20the%20bridge%20and%20is%20responsible%20for%20its%20maintenance%20and%20upgrades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20health%20check-up%20of%20the%20bridge%20was%20conducted%20between%201983%20and%201988%2C%20after%20it%20remained%20in%20operation%20for%2040%20years%2C%20an%20SMP%2C%20Kolkata%20official%20said.%20The%20latest%20health%20check-up%20will%20be%20conducted%20by%20RITES%20Ltd%2C%20a%20public%20sector%20undertaking%20that%20is%20tasked%20with%20the%20maintenance%20of%20the%20Howrah%20Bridge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bridge%2C%20a%20suspension-type%20balanced%20cantilever%20structure%2C%20is%20the%20sixth%20longest%20of%20its%20kind%20in%20the%20world.%20Despite%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Vidyasagar%20Setu%20across%20Hooghly%2C%20the%20Howrah%20Bridge%20remains%20one%20of%20the%20busiest%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20estimated%20100%2C000%20vehicles%20and%201%2C50%2C000%20pedestrians%20cross%20the%20bridge%20daily.%20What%20makes%20the%20bridge%20so%20alluring%20is%20its%20proximity%20to%20the%20Howrah%20railway%20station%20--%20one%20of%20the%20busiest%20in%20the%20world%20--%20which%20is%20still%20considered%20a%20gateway%20to%20Kolkata.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20comprehensive%20health%20check-up%20of%20the%20bridge%20is%20important%20as%20it%20handles%20so%20much%20traffic.%20It%20is%20an%20iconic%20structure%20that%20has%20captured%20the%20imagination%20of%20artists%2C%20filmmakers%20and%20the%20common%20man.%20No%20illustration%20of%20Kolkata%20is%20complete%20without%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Howrah%20Bridge%20peeping%20out%20from%20somewhere%20in%20the%20frame.%20The%20bridge%20was%20commissioned%20in%201943%20during%20World%20War%20II%2C%20even%20as%20the%20Japanese%20were%20bombing%20Kolkata%20(then%20Calcutta).%20To%20keep%20the%20bridge%20safe%20from%20Japanese%20bombers%2C%20the%20commissioning%20was%20done%20at%20night%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bridge%20also%20brought%20into%20focus%20the%20capability%20of%20Indian%20industry%20to%20produce%20high-quality%20tensile%20steel%2C%20even%20under%20British%20rule.%20Construction%20of%20the%20bridge%20started%20with%20steel%20sent%20from%20England.%20This%20supply%20had%20to%20be%20stopped%20though%20as%20steel%20produced%20in%20England%20was%20required%20for%20the%20war%20effort.%20It%20was%20Tata%20Steel%20that%20came%20up%20with%20tensile%20steel%20of%20the%20quality%20required%20for%20the%20Bridge%20and%20the%20rest%20is%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHence%2C%20we%20are%20really%20proud%20of%20this%20Bridge%20that%20was%20built%20with%20high-quality%20steel%20produced%20by%20an%20Indian%20manufacturer%2C%20even%20when%20the%20country%20was%20under%20colonial%20rule.%20We%20would%20like%20Howrah%20Bridge%20to%20remain%20in%20service%20for%20several%20more%20decades%2C%20hence%20the%20health%20check-up%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731741360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-01%2Fkolkata-howrah-bridge-istock-photo_650x400_61451884593.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkolkata-news%2Fkolkatas-iconic-howrah-bridge-to-shut-for-5-hours-for-health-checkup-7028166%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%2081-year-old%20iconic%20Howrah%20Bridge%20(Rabindra%20Setu)%20--%20t