o%20create%20their%20own%20family%20traditions%20as%20a%20married%20couple.%20With%20Alba%20hailing%20from%20Portugal%2C%20the%20couple%20is%20planning%20to%20celebrate%20Christmas%20alternately%20between%20Massachusetts%20and%20Portugal.%20Chris%20revealed%20they%20recently%20got%20a%20home%20in%20Portugal%2C%20where%20they%20are%20excited%20to%20build%20fresh%20memories%20and%20traditions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Fchris-evans-shares-hopes-of-becoming-a-dad%2Farticleshow%2F115354473.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Iran's%20Message%20To%20US%3A%20No%20Intent%20To%20Assassinate%20Donald%20Trump%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIran%20has%20sent%20a%20message%20to%20the%20Joe%20Biden%20administration%20denying%20any%20plans%20to%20kill%20Donald%20Trump.%20This%20development%20comes%20after%20the%20Biden%20administration%20warned%20Iran%20in%20September%20that%20any%20attempt%20on%20Mr%20Trump's%20life%20would%20be%20considered%20%E2%80%9Can%20act%20of%20war%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F11%2F15%2Fworld%2Fmiddleeast%2Firan-trump-assassinate.html%C2%A0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENY%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20message%2C%20sent%20in%20October%20through%20an%20intermediary%2C%20was%20intended%20to%20ease%20tensions%20between%20Washington%20and%20Tehran.%20It%20followed%20a%20stern%20warning%20from%20the%20US%2C%20which%20had%20expressed%20grave%20concerns%20over%20potential%20Iranian%20retaliation%20for%20the%20killing%20of%20Maj.%20Gen.%20Qassim%20Suleimani%20in%202020%2C%20a%20move%20ordered%20by%20then-President%20Donald%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ESince%20Donald%20Trump's%20election%20victory%20on%20November%205%2C%20various%20Iranian%20officials%2C%20analysts%2C%20and%20media%20outlets%20have%20advocated%20for%20a%20more%20conciliatory%20approach%20with%20the%20president-elect%2C%20despite%20ongoing%20pressure%20from%20his%20allies%20to%20renew%20a%20hardline%20stance%20against%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EUS%20officials%20have%20suggested%20that%20Iran%20may%20have%20sought%20revenge%20for%20Suleimani's%20death%20by%20targeting%20Mr%20Trump%2C%20citing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F3rd-assassination-attempt-iran-man-charged-with-plotting-to-kill-trump-6977316%C2%A0%5C%22%3Etwo%20indictments%20related%20to%20Iranian%20plots%20against%20the%C2%A0President-elect%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Further%20accusations%20have%20surfaced%20regarding%20other%20figures%20from%20the%20Trump%20administration.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20the%20US%20officials%2C%20the%20Iranian%20message%20focused%20on%20Tehran's%20position%20that%20the%20killing%20of%20General%20Suleimani%20was%20a%20criminal%20act.%20However%2C%20the%20communication%20also%20clarified%20that%20Iran%20had%20no%20intention%20of%20killing%20Trump.%20This%20message%20was%20confirmed%20by%20an%20Iranian%20official%20and%20analyst%20who%20engages%20with%20both%20sides.%20Iran%2C%20they%20said%2C%20expressed%20its%20desire%20to%20pursue%20justice%20for%20Suleimani's%20death%20through%20international%20legal%20channels%20rather%20than%20through%20violent%20means.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWhile%20the%20US%20officials%20noted%20that%20the%20message%20was%20not%20from%20any%20specific%20Iranian%20official%2C%20the%20Iranian%20official%20and%20analyst%20revealed%20that%20it%20was%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20from%20Iran's%20Supreme%20Leader%2C%20Ayatollah%20Ali%20Khamenei.%20Iran's%20mission%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%20declined%20to%20comment%20but%20issued%20a%20statement%20reaffirming%20Tehran's%20commitment%20to%20addressing%20Suleimani's%20killing%20%26quot%3Bthrough%20legal%20and%20judicial%20avenues.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EEarlier%2C%20during%20the%20presidential%20campaign%2C%20American%20officials%20had%20warned%20of%20a%20potential%20Iranian%20plot%20to%20assassinate%20Donald%20Trump.%20Federal%20prosecutors%20in%20Manhattan%20recently%20confirmed%20that%20discussions%20among%20Iranian%20plotters%20had%20included%20plans%20to%20target%20the%20former%20president.%20However%2C%20Iran's%20Foreign%20Ministry%20rejected%20these%20claims%20as%20unfounded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%2C%20a%20close%20ally%20of%20Mr%20Trump%2C%20met%20with%20Iran's%20ambassador%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%20on%20Monday%20at%20Mr%20Musk's%20request.%20The%20Iranians%20described%20the%20meeting%20with%20Ambassador%20Amir%20Saied%20Iravani%2C%20held%20in%20New%20York%20City%20at%20a%20secret%20location%2C%20as%20part%20of%20an%20effort%20to%20reduce%20tensions%20between%20the%20US%20and%20Iran%20under%20the%20Donald%20Trump%20administration.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20US%20and%20Iran%20have%20not%20had%20official%20diplomatic%20relations%20since%20the%201979%20revolution%2C%20during%20which%2052%20Americans%20were%20taken%20hostage%20at%20the%20US%20embassy%20in%20Tehran.%20The%20Swiss%20embassy%20in%20Tehran%20serves%20as%20the%20official%20diplomatic%20liaison%20between%20the%20two%20countries%2C%20though%20direct%20and%20indirect%20talks%20have%20taken%20place%20in%20recent%20years%20on%20various%20issues%2C%20including%20Iran's%20nuclear%20program%20and%20the%20swapping%20of%20detainees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20messages%20exchanged%20between%20the%20US%20and%20Iran%20were%20sent%20through%20the%20Swiss%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Iranian%20official%20and%20analyst.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731740160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.nd