80%99s%20involvement.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20real%20impact%20comes%20from%20students%2C%20families%2C%20and%20communities%20coming%20together%20to%20make%20this%20project%20a%20success%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPrevious%20generations%20understood%20the%20importance%20of%20sparrows%2C%20but%20today%E2%80%99s%20generation%20is%20less%20aware%20of%20how%20vital%20they%20are%20for%20human%20survival.%20Unfortunately%2C%20the%20general%20public%20often%20lacks%20the%20time%20or%20interest%20to%20learn%20about%20their%20significance.%20This%20is%20why%20we%20decided%20to%20focus%20on%20schools%2C%20to%20raise%20awareness%20and%20explain%20the%20mission%20of%20Koodugal%20Nest%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20founder%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201152px)%20100vw%2C%201152px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-05-at-22.32.15-1-1731592215.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221152%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ganeshan%20focuses%20on%20schools%20to%20raise%20awareness%20about%20sparrow%20conservation%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-05-at-22.32.15-1-1731592215.jpeg%201152w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-05-at-22.32.15-1-1731592215-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-05-at-22.32.15-1-1731592215-500x281.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-05-at-22.32.15-1-1731592215-768x432.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-05-at-22.32.15-1-1731592215-150x84.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-379974%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22648%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EGaneshan%20focuses%20on%20schools%20to%20raise%20awareness%20about%20sparrow%20conservation%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20significant%20discovery%20the%20NGO%20made%20was%20that%20the%20reduction%20in%20sand%20in%20urban%20areas%20was%20a%20major%20factor%20in%20the%20sparrow%20population%20decline.%20In%202020%2C%20at%20Revoor%20Padmanabha%20Chetty%20Matriculation%20Higher%20Secondary%20School%20in%20Tiruvottiyur%2C%20the%20abundance%20of%20sand%20made%20it%20the%20perfect%20environment%20for%20sparrows.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20installing%20100%20nest%20boxes%20on%20the%20school%20campus%2C%20the%20results%20were%20immediate.%20%E2%80%9CWithin%20six%20months%2C%20most%20of%20the%20boxes%20were%20occupied%2C%20and%20today%2C%20100%25%20of%20the%20nest%20boxes%20are%20in%20use%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ganeshan%20proudly%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20dedicate%20our%20time%20to%20conserving%20sparrows%20because%20as%20their%20population%20grows%2C%20they%20will%20help%20control%20mosquitoes%2C%20cockroaches%2C%20and%20other%20small%20insects%20that%20often%20go%20unnoticed.%20Sparrows%20thrive%20close%20to%20human%20settlements%2C%20as%20they%20can%20only%20survive%20in%20temperatures%20that%20are%20ideal%20for%20us%2C%20not%20in%20extremes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEmpowering%20the%20next%20generation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKoodugal%20Trust%20has%20made%20a%20significant%20impact%20on%20students.%20Sharing%20her%20experience%2C%20Prayukta%2C%20a%2014-year-old%20student%20from%20RPC%20Matriculation%20School%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20was%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Koodugal%20Nest%20project%2C%20and%20he%20brought%20home%20a%20nest%20in%202022.%20We%20all%20helped%20in%20installing%20it%2C%20and%20it%20was%20amazing%20to%20watch%20sparrows%20take%20care%20of%20their%20young%20ones.%20I%20have%20developed%20a%20habit%20of%20feeding%20them%20and