0who%20can%20play%20the%20kamaicha.%20Same%20is%20the%20case%20with%20sarangi%2C%20alghoza%2C%20and%20morchang%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Govind%20Singh%20Bhati.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGrowing%20up%2C%20I%20was%20naturally%20exposed%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20folk%20music%20because%20of%20where%20I%20come%20from.%20My%20father%20loved%20playing%20the%20%3Cem%3Emorchang%3C%2Fem%3E%20(jaw%20harp)%20and%20%3Cem%3Ealghoza%20%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20pair%20of%20joined%20beak%20flutes%20that%20are%20played%20simultaneously)%2C%20and%20my%20grandfather%20would%20often%20sit%20with%20the%20artists%20and%20join%20in%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bhati%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20early%20experiences%20helped%20him%20understand%20the%20essence%20and%20significance%20of%20folk%20music%20%E2%80%94%20its%20origins%20and%20its%20deep%20connection%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Rajasthan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20mission%20to%20preserve%20traditional%20arts%20for%20future%20generations%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%202008-09%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20become%20an%20independent%20arts%20manager%20for%20Rajasthani%20artists%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bhati%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20few%20years%2C%20he%20collaborated%20with%20event%20organisers%20across%20the%20state%20and%20worked%20with%20institutions%20like%20the%20Mehrangarh%20Trust%20and%20Jaipur%20Virasat%20Foundation%2C%20all%20of%20which%20were%20actively%20providing%20platforms%20for%20folk%20artists%20to%20showcase%20their%20talents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20Bhati%2C%20along%20with%20Sharon%20Genevive%2C%20launched%20%E2%80%98BlueCity%20Walls%E2%80%99%2C%20through%20which%20they%20collaborated%20with%20artists%2C%20organised%20shows%2C%20and%20conducted%20tours%20of%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F287963%2Firish-man-revives-cleans-stepwells-in-jodhpur-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Jodhpur%E2%80%99s%20old%20city%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20employing%20local%20residents%20in%20the%20process.%20As%20their%20work%20with%20artists%20progressed%2C%20the%20couple%20realised%20that%20much%20of%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20folk%20music%20was%20slowly%20fading%20away.%20With%20the%20older%20generation%20passing%20on%2C%20the%20younger%20generation%20lacked%20a%20formal%20way%20to%20learn%20and%20preserve%20these%20traditional%20art%20forms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202750px)%20100vw%2C%202750px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FTCH03486-1_11zon-1731068934.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222750%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bringing%20Rajasthani%20folk%20music%20to%20life%3A%20Children%20and%20musicians%20from%20Langa%2C%20Meghwal%2C%20and%20Manganiyar%20communities%20unite%20in%20harmony%2C%20preserving%20and%20celebrating%20their%20cultural%20heritage.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FTCH03486-1_11zon-1731068934.jpg%202750w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FTCH03486-1_11zon-1731068934-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FTCH03486-1_11zon-1731068934-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FTCH03486-1_11zon-1731068934-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FTCH03486-1_11zon-1731068934-1536x1024.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FTCH03486-1_11zon-1731068934-2048x1365.jpg%20204