portunities%20%3C%2Fa%3Efor%20live%20music%20sessions.%20This%20initiative%20ensured%20that%20the%20artists%20were%20fairly%20compensated%2C%20while%20also%20driving%20increased%20app%20traffic%20and%20downloads.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20just%20had%20to%20sit%20at%20home%20and%20do%20some%20of%20the%20work%2C%20so%20we%20were%20fine%20doing%20it%20for%20free%2C%20but%20the%20artists%20needed%20to%20be%20paid%20%E2%80%94%20that%20was%20our%20only%20condition%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Bhati.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20peak%20months%20of%20COVID-19%2C%20they%20successfully%20hosted%20live%20sessions%20on%20the%20app%2C%20allowing%20every%20participating%20artist%20to%20receive%20compensation.%20This%20initiative%20also%20encouraged%20greater%20involvement%20from%20women%2C%20as%20it%20eliminated%20the%20need%20for%20them%20to%20travel%2C%20enabling%20those%20who%20had%20only%20sung%20for%20their%20families%20to%20showcase%20their%20talent%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202448px)%20100vw%2C%202448px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FLSS-2018-1-1_11zon-1731068846.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222448%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20experienced%20Rajasthani%20folk%20artist%20teaching%20young%20children%20the%20intricacies%20of%20traditional%20music%20at%20the%20Lok%20Sangeet%20Shala%20residency%2C%20promoting%20cultural%20preservation%20and%20knowledge%20transfer.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FLSS-2018-1-1_11zon-1731068846.jpg%202448w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FLSS-2018-1-1_11zon-1731068846-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FLSS-2018-1-1_11zon-1731068846-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FLSS-2018-1-1_11zon-173106884