ther)%20herself%20to%20teach%20the%20nuances%20of%20making%20a%20good%20ol%E2%80%99%20helping%20of%20this%20timeless%20winter%20edition%20staple%3F%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EThandi%20ke%20mausam%20mein%20undhiya%20garam%20garam%20puri%20aur%20thanda%20thanda%20shrikhand%20khane%20mein%20sabko%20majja%20aata%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(In%20winter%2C%20everyone%20loves%20eating%20%3Cem%3Eundhiyu%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewith%20hot%20%3Cem%3Epuris%20%3C%2Fem%3E(deep%20fried%20bread)%20and%20cold%20%3Cem%3Eshrikhand%3C%2Fem%3E%20(traditional%20Indian%20sweet))%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20smiles%2C%20as%20she%20busies%20herself%20listing%20out%20the%20ingredients%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEighty-year-old%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F268194%2Fgujju-ben-na-nasta-mumbai-best-breakfast-inspiring-woman-entrepreneur-grandmother-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUrmila%20Asher%20helms%20%E2%80%98Gujju%20Ben%20Na%20Nasta%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20brand%20that%20prides%20itself%20on%20homemade%20Gujarati%20snacks.%20And%20today%20she%20is%20here%20to%20ensure%20your%20%3Cem%3Eundhiyu%20%3C%2Fem%3Eturns%20out%20perfect.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FDMDYZRskPB8%3Fsi%3DYYqi0RKJHuWaz5rb%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20%E2%80%98poster%20dish%E2%80%99%20of%20Gujarati%20cuisine%2C%20whose%20appearance%20on%20the%20dinner%20%3Cem%3Ethali%20%3C%2Fem%3E(plate)%20is%20indicative%20of%20winter%20onset%2C%20goes%20beyond%20being%20a%20delicious%20addition.%20Prepared%20with%20seasonal%20vegetables%2C%20such%20as%20brinjals%2C%20green%20beans%2C%20and%20sweet%20potatoes%2C%20the%20dish%20packs%20a%20punch%20in%20every%20mouthful.%20While%20every%20region%20has%20its%20unique%20spin%20on%20th